::Magmatron/Jynx/Nemean Hydra::

    Magmatron made Jynx awake. As Jynx ste=
pped out he was in his beast mode, the same as Dachande's. Magmatron ordere=
d him to go to and help in the fight. He ran out of the base in his new for=
m.
    Then Magmatron ordered Nemean Hydra to go to the lab. The Beast did,=
 and once there Magmatron made sure that the bot was out of it. Then Magmat=
ron started to make his new body. It was going to be the same as Jynx and D=
achande's beast mode, but something went wrong, the body mutated, it became=
 somewhat like the other creature that was sitting in another lab now, but =
smaller, less powerful. And it didn't have a robot mode. But Magmatron didn=
't care, he started the spark transfer.

Jynx:
